American Teenager Christina McHale Loses to Kirilenko in US Open 3rd Round

-- B y   R o b   G l o s t e r
-- 
2011-09-03T00:55:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-03/american-teenager-christina-mchale-loses-to-kirilenko-in-us-open-3rd-round.html
American teenager Christina McHale
lost in the third round of the U.S. Open, a straight-set defeat
by  Maria Kirilenko .  McHale, 19, from Englewood Cliffs,  New Jersey , lost 6-2, 6-
3 tonight to the 25th-seeded Russian. In the previous round,
McHale upset No. 8 Marion Bartoli of  France .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rob Gloster at 
 rgloster@bloomberg.net  